  <span id="freeText16742002650104045966" style="display:none">A new favorite Melanie Dickerson book!! 😁 Loved that the main characters had known each other since they were kids. It was a fun read to me 😊 I accidently read this before the Silent Songbird somehow 😅 but I'm hoping it'll be okay. For those who've read both of these, do you think it matters I read this first? </span>
